I '''Dean Ray Koontz''' (mibait Julio 9, 1945) Americanu yang talasulat libru. King maleparang salita, malyari lang ausang [[suspense thriller]] deng karelang libru, oneng maki elementu la mu naman ning [[horror fiction|horror]], [[science fiction]], [[Mystery (fiction)|mystery]], ampong [[satira]]. Mibili no reng mapilan kareng kayang libru king [[New York Times Bestseller List|''New York Times'' Bestseller List]], at 14 kareng hardcover<ref name="nyt chart toppers">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2012/01/15/books/review/bestsellers-weekly-graphic.html|title=Koontz’s Chart Toppers|date=January 11, 2012 |accessdate=January 29, 2012|publisher=''[[New York Times]]''}}</ref> ampong 14 a paperback ing miras king mumunang pwestu.<ref name="deankoontz.com">{{cite web|title=http://www.deankoontz.com/about-dean/}}</ref> Anyang mumunang dake ning kayang karera, sinulat ya i Koontz king lalam da reng mapilang [[talipampan]], kayabe la reng "David Axton", "Leigh Nichols" ampong "Brian Coffey".
He has sold over 450 million copies as reported on his official site.

